title: [JAZZ PIANO] Hampton Hawes Trio Vol.1 (1955)
description:
Hampton Hawes Trio, Vol. 1 (1955)

HAMPTON HAWES - piano
RED MITCHELL - bass
CHUCK THOMPSON - drums

Recorded in Los Angeles; June 28, 1955

This is jazz piano legend Hampton Hawes&#039; first recording with his trio for Contemporary records. His breathtaking solo on "I Got Rhythm" is one of the best solos ever played on a rhythm-changes-type tune. If you&#039;re a jazz musician, this is a great solo to transcribe!
